{"type":null,"faqId":36952,"title":"奖励怎么使用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>父母可以通过“奖励”功能设定奖励目标，包括孩子需要获得的表扬次数及获得这些次数的表扬后可以得到的奖励内容。孩子获得规定次数的表扬后，父母需要按照设定的奖励内容给孩子奖励。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在APP主右下角点击“奖励”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121226\" style=\"width:2.7743056in;height:4.3618054in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.设置孩子需要获得的表扬次数及获得这些次数的表扬后可以得到的奖励内容。表扬次数达到目标后，APP提示目标完成，可以设置新任务。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121227\" style=\"width:2.7784722in;height:4.35in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.需要表扬孩子时，点击“表扬一下”对孩子进行表扬。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121228\" style=\"width:2.7777777in;height:4.370139in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>4.表扬次数达到目标后，APP提示目标完成。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121229\" style=\"width:2.7784722in;height:4.3555555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>5.已完成的任务，可以在历史记录里查看</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121230\" style=\"width:2.7784722in;height:4.3548613in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>父母在APP上表扬宝贝，手表会收到提示。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121231\" style=\"width:1.3319445in;height:1.3319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2052","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440638665000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":6,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀小K,儿童,手表","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}